channel.title: Complexity - Just oldschool without new items
channel.description:
[center][b]Welcome to Complexity, [/b] we are a new oldschool private server that was put online recently. To play Complexity you must just click "Play" or "Download" button, once you have downloaded Complexity all you have to do is launch the .jar file and the game will load! How do you earn money in Complexity? there is multiple ways to do it one is to go out there and fight monsters which drops money caskets, collect the caskets and you make good money! One way is to support our server and Donate for us, to donate for Complexity just simply click the 'Donate' button and follow what it says. By donating you don't just help Complexity but you buy your self items/money & other goodies. We really hope you a pleasant play with us!
[url=http://www.complexityrsps.com]Home[/url] [url=http://www.complexityrsps.com/play]Play now[/url] [url=http://www.complexityrsps.com/complexity.jar]Download client[/url] [url=http://www.complexityrsps.com/vote]Vote[/url]
